Class SimpleMinimalOntology

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.ontology.data.impl.SimpleMinimalOntology
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, MinimalOntology, Versioned
public class SimpleMinimalOntology extends Object implements MinimalOntology
SimpleMinimalOntology implements MinimalOntology with an OntologyGraph and Maps of Terms and Relationships.
